Michael Fennell, the President of the Commonwealth Games Federation, says that the Games will go ahead but that there "was extensive work to be done" for the 2010 Commonwealth Games in Delhi, India, ahead of its opening on 3 October. (Reuters) (Al Jazeera)Boston Red Sox owner John W. Henry agrees to purchase Liverpool F.C. for an undisclosed sum, the deal still needs final approval. (Boston.com),(Sky News)